/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八婆健吾唔撚抵得人揾位入姐"},{"pid":"63ee73b47467fa20339a0bd7b637842e06ea687e","tid":46114,"uid":45217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"佢真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想捧戇鳩坤都唔係咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d19fb295d431e154a0bb7f60c5058647507190b","tid":46114,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"講到投坤哥先係清泉咁撚樣<br />\n<br />\n講到努力就一定要俾坤哥冧莊<br />\n<br />\n講到陳奕迅張敬軒拎到我最喜愛都唔及坤哥咁值<br />\n<br />\n偏頗到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558f580a7c2b901bb1d3b9182a7267ae2eac920f","tid":46114,"uid":50298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時講憎，點解</blockquote><br />\n係囉 有冇醬油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳柏宇係演唱會嗰時話唔鍾意舊歌啲style大部分都係啲消極既情歌，雖然嗰啲歌既曲詞都好好，但佢自己鍾意啲正面啲有啲正能量既歌，好似乜青嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n我唔覺得佢咁講有咩問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八婆健吾唔撚抵得人揾位入姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斷章取義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ad23dea8df675f86fdf4f3e255b28ba3233711","tid":46114,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想捧戇鳩坤都唔係咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早話佢成個撚屌咁款唔方好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2915021d1575d71750e376a824be888b251eded1","tid":46114,"uid":18717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時講憎，點解</blockquote><br />\n係囉 有冇醬油</blockquote><br />\